CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Nektar Therapeutics is a biopharmaceutical company. It has wholly-owned research and development pipeline of investigational medicines in oncology, immunology, and virology as well as a portfolio of approved partnered medicines. The company has additional operations facilities in Huntsville, Alabama, and Hyderabad, India.
